title: Hour 1 - Winners & Losers from Week 3, Ross Tucker

description:
Dan dissects the winners and losers from week 3 of the NFL and considers which teams are underperforming so far. And NFL Insider Ross Tucker swings by to lend his expertise to the discussion.
